  "texts": [
    "When considering the best model for each technique, in-context learning increases the percentage of contextualized responses by 5%.",
    "These results greatly differ from Table 2 and show how unreliable automatic evaluation can be.",
    "Although models fine-tuned on No or Retrieved Knowledge obtain comparable or higher validity than in-context learning, adding Gold Knowledge to adapt Llama2 C and Mistral I with in-context learning increases their validity respectively by 5% and 10%.",
    "Finally, even with Gold Knowledge, no model reaches the validity of the ground truth (90%).",
    "These findings indicate that the best technique depends on the dialogue type and the base LLM."
  ],
